    "en": {
      "title": "Three million successfully registered for \u2019National Fuel Pass\u2019",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of people who have successfully registered themselves to obtain National Fuel Passes has exceeded 3,000,000 by last evening (in four days), the Power and Energy Ministry said.",
        "This system was introduced yesterday and will be upgraded in the next few days to give an option for businesses and organizations that operate multiple vehicles to register their full fleet of vehicles using the Business Registration Number, the Ministry said.",
        "The National Fuel Pass portal was officially launched on Saturday (16) by the Power and Energy Ministry for easy and efficient fuel distribution.",
        "The first-time user should visit the fuel quota management portal available on the http://fuelpass.gov.lk. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
